729960f-a.title: Richmond: Woodrow Road - Bloomingdale Road
729960f-a.text:
Woodrow Road, at the S.E. corner of Bloomingdale Road,
showing the C. Bogardus house (1874-1907 maps). The view is
south on Bloomingdale Road.
May 30, 1932
P. L. Sperr
